 giường King Size sang trọng, cuộn tròn trên ghế sofa bên trang sách hay tận hưởng không gian làm việc rộng rãi. Những chọn lựa ẩm thực với thực đơn ngon lành phục vụ tại phòng, bồn tắm rộng và dịch vụ dọn phòng ban đêm sẽ mang đến cho bạn một trải nghiệm đầy tươi mới và yên tĩnh.','admin','::1','2017-11-22 00:30:19'),(803,'room_manages',1,'description_en','Update','Miễn phí ăn sáng và bãi tắm','Warm colors and rich woods set the tone in our Executive rooms – restful and relaxing havens carefully crafted for the modern traveler. Sink into the luxurious King bed, curl up on the sofa with a good book, or stay on top of it all in a spacious work area. Add to this a host of delectable in-room dining options, a spacious bathtub and nightly turndown service, and a rejuvenating and restful stay is guaranteed.','admin','::1','2017-11-22 00:30:19'),(804,'room_manages',3,'description_en','Update','Miễn phí ăn sáng và bãi tắm','With stunning city views, a plush King bed, large Jacuzzi bathtub and endless opportunities for rest and rejuvenation, our Silver Suites offer all the comforts of home right at the heart of Saigon. We invite you to settle in, stretch out and make this expansive space your own. An elegant living area invites with chaise longue, coffee table and ample working space; perfect for planning your next day’s Saigon adventures. Come evening, plush pillows, luxurious linens and our nightly turndown service will lull you into blissful relaxation.','admin','::1','2017-11-22 00:30:47'),(805,'room_manages',1,'bedding','Update','1','1 double Beds','admin','::1','2017-11-22 00:32:10'),(806,'room_manages',1,'price','Update','900000','782,609','admin','::1','2017-11-22 00:32:10'),(807,'room_manages',2,'description_en','Update','Miễn phí ăn sáng và bãi tắm','Our Premier rooms deliver urban serenity at its best. Take in vivid views of the Saigon streets below from a haven of peace and calm. Choose from a bathtub or spacious freestanding shower and Twin or King beds and let the warm décor, luxurious furnishings and nightly turndown service lull you into sweet relaxation after a busy day of sightseeing.','admin','::1','2017-11-22 00:33:17'),(808,'room_manages',2,'bedding','Update','1','2 Single Beds or 1 King Bed','admin','::1','2017-11-22 00:33:17'),(809,'room_manages',2,'price','Update','1300000','1,304,348','admin','::1','2017-11-22 00:33:17'),(810,'room_holidayprice',10,'Trash','Trash','','','admin','::1','2017-11-22 00:33:40'),(811,'room_holidayprice',8,'Trash','Trash','','','admin','::1','2017-11-22 00:33:40'),(812,'room_holidayprice',7,'Trash','Trash','','','admin','::1','2017-11-22 00:33:40'),(813,'room_holidayprice',10,'Delete','Delete','','','admin','::1','2017-11-22 00:33:44'),(814,'room_holidayprice',8,'Delete','Delete','','','admin','::1','2017-11-22 00:33:44'),(815,'room_holidayprice',7,'Delete','Delete','','','admin','::1','2017-11-22 00:33:44'),(816,'room_holidayprice',11,'Add new','Add new','','','admin','::1','2017-11-22 00:34:53'),(817,'room_holidayprice',12,'Add new','Add new','','','admin','::1','2017-11-22 00:35:20'),(818,'room_holidayprice',12,'date','Update','2017-11-25 00:00:00','2017/12/25','admin','::1','2017-11-22 00:35:40'),(819,'room_holidayprice',13,'Add new','Add new','','','admin','::1','2017-11-22 00:36:49'),(820,'room_holidayprice',14,'Add new','Add new','','','admin','::1','2017-11-22 00:37:16'),(821,'room_offers',4,'Trash','Trash','','','admin','::1','2017-11-22 00:38:35'),(822,'room_offers',3,'Trash','Trash','','','admin','::1','2017-11-22 00:38:35'),(823,'room_offers',3,'Delete','Delete','','','admin','::1','2017-11-22 00:38:40'),(824,'room_offers',4,'Delete','Delete','','','admin','::1','2017-11-22 00:38:40'),(825,'room_manages',2,'price','Update','1,304,348','1304348','admin','::1','2017-11-22 11:51:33'),(826,'room_manages',1,'price','Update','782,609','782609','admin','::1','2017-11-22 11:51:45'),(827,'room_offers',6,'title_vn','Update','Rom & dinner so romantic ( save 20%)','Dinner so romantic